character.name: Spy
character.description: At the end of the round, if you are the only player in the round who played or discarded a Spy, gain 1 favor token.

character.name: Guard
character.description: Choose another player and name a non-Guard card. If that player has that card, they are out of the round.

character.name: Priest
character.description: Choose and look at another player's hand.

character.name: Baron
character.description: Choose and secretly compare hands with another player. Whoever has the lower value is out of the round.

character.name: Handmaid
character.description: Until your next turn, other players cannot choose you for their card effects.

character.name: Prince
character.description: Choose any player (including yourself). That player discards their hand and redraws.

character.name: Chancellor
character.description: Draw 2 cards. Keep 1 card and put your other 2 on the bottom of the deck in any order.

character.name: King
character.description: Choose and trade hands with another player.

character.name: Countess
character.description: If the King or Prince is in your hand, you must play this card.

character.name: Princess
character.description: If you play or discard this card, you are out of the round.
